
# --------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Software Requeriments
# --------------------------------------------------------------------------------

You'll need these to modify and run ForGAtran:

- Eclipse Classic 3.6.1 IDE or higher
- Photran
- Intel® Fortran Compiler (working to make gnu fortran work)


Download and install: Eclipse Classic 3.6.1 IDE
http://www.eclipse.org/downloads/

Download and install: Photran - An Integrated Development Environment and Refactoring Tool for Fortran
http://www.eclipse.org/photran/

Note: You can download and install Photran though Eclipse

Download and install: Noncommercial Intel® Fortran Compiler Professional Edition for Linux
http://software.intel.com/en-us/articles/non-commercial-software-download/



